      "span_text": "The first article, by Kwa and Muggia, is a historical review of trials of intraperitoneal chemotherapy for patients with ovarian malignancies. Despite landmark trials such as the GOG 172, which clearly showed survival benefit for patients receiving regional therapy with intraperitoneal paclitaxel, there appears to a relative reluctance of practitioners to adopt this technique widely."
